title: Mr Boukadoum holds talks with his Cuban counterpart
text: The Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr. Sabri Boukadoum, held Tuesday a phone call with his Cuban counterpart, Mr. Bruno Rodriguez Parrilla.

The two ministers reviewed the historical relations between the two countries, and the means to extend them to all fields. The interview also focused on international and regional issues of common interest and others related to international cooperation in the fight against Covid-19.
